title: Can Amy Let Her Kids Watch The Cosby Show? + Bobby’s Date Fell Through + Raymundo Grilled For Missing Proposal Deadline
itunes:title: Can Amy Let Her Kids Watch The Cosby Show? + Bobby’s Date Fell Through + Raymundo Grilled For Missing Proposal Deadline
description:
Amy saw that The Cosby Show is available on Amazon and wants to know if it’s okay to let her kids watch it after what Bill Cosby did. Bobby had a date fall through because he didn’t check-in on the day of the date and she assumed it was off. Also, Raymundo missed his “Summer of Love” proposal deadline, but has a new month picked out.
